Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.29,0:28:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概巴也在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.04,0:28:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决他们
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.74,0:28:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…

